description: Lists all of the DataBrew projects that are defined.

nested_items.name: Projects
nested_items.description: A list of projects that are defined .

nested_items.name: AccountId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that owns the project.

nested_items.name: CreateDate
nested_items.description: The date and time that the project was created.

nested_items.name: CreatedBy
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the user who crated the project.

nested_items.name: DatasetName
nested_items.description: The dataset that the project is to act upon.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedDate
nested_items.description: The last modification date and time for the project.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedBy
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the user who last modified the project.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The unique name of a project.

nested_items.name: RecipeName
nested_items.description: The name of a recipe that will be developed during a project session.

nested_items.name: ResourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the project.

nested_items.name: Size
nested_items.description: The number of rows in the sample.

nested_items.name: Type
nested_items.description: The way in which DataBrew obtains rows from a dataset.

nested_items.name: RoleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the role that will be assumed for this project.

nested_items.name: OpenedBy
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the user that opened the project for use.

nested_items.name: OpenDate
nested_items.description: The date and time when the project was opened.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token that you can use in a subsequent call to retrieve the next set of results.
